---
const reg =
  "sopsy recipient add break-glass --public-key age1q... --break-glass";
---

<section class="section section--tight">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="breakglass" data-reveal>
      <div class="breakglass__grid">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow eyebrow--amber">Break-glass keys</p>
          <h3>Set up disaster recovery on day one.</h3>
          <p>
            A break-glass key is a separate emergency age key pair, stored <b
              >offline</b
            > in a vault and shared with only a few admins. If every developer's Secure
            Enclave device is lost, it can still decrypt and re-key the repository.
          </p>
          <p style="margin-top:1rem">
            Lose your only Enclave device with no break-glass key, and every
            secret becomes <b>permanently undecryptable</b>. That's why <code
              class="mono amber">doctor</code
            > and <code class="mono amber">check</code> nag until one exists — and
            sopsy refuses to remove the sole break-glass recipient.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="terminal">
            <div class="terminal__bar">
              <div class="terminal__dots"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
              <span class="terminal__title">offline · once</span>
            </div>
            <div class="terminal__body">
              <span class="ln cmt"
                ># generate an emergency key pair OFFLINE</span
              >
              <span class="ln prompt">age-keygen -o break-glass.key</span>
              <span class="ln key"> public key: age1q… ← register this</span>
              <span class="ln cmt"
                ># store break-glass.key in 1Password / a vault</span
              >
              <span class="ln cmt"></span>
              <span class="ln cmt"
                ># register it as the break-glass recipient</span
              >
              <span class="ln prompt">sopsy recipient add break-glass \</span>
              <span class="ln"> --public-key age1q… --break-glass</span>
              <span class="ln ok">
                ✔ re-encrypted 3 files for new recipient set</span
              >
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
